Having confirmed that HOMER3 , DNCL1 and TRIM11 interact with the PAX6 PST domain , we next investigated how the interactions were affected by three <termsem="CHEBI:18245"> <termsem="CHEBI:46883"> C </term> </term> - terminal PAX6 mutations that have been previously described in patients with ocular anomalies .
